...the way you do all of them.

853
01:14:20,593 --> 01:14:22,993
还有露易莎，我还不太了解她
Louisa, I don't know about yet.

854
01:14:23,262 --> 01:14:26,459
这些小孩只想要被爱 求求你，舰长，爱他们
The little ones just want love. Please, love them all.

855
01:14:26,732 --> 01:14:28,256
我不想再听你说有关孩子的事
I don't care to hear more.

856
01:14:28,501 --> 01:14:32,597
-我还没说完 -是的，你说完了，舰长
- I am not finished yet, captain! - Oh, yes, you are, captain!

857
01:14:34,140 --> 01:14:35,300
小姐
Fraulein.

858
01:14:36,609 --> 01:14:40,739
你现在立刻收拾行李
Now, you will pack your things this minute...

859
01:14:40,947 --> 01:14:43,438
回去修道院
...and return to the abbey.

860
01:14:46,085 --> 01:14:47,416
那是什么？
What's that?

861
01:14:49,155 --> 01:14:50,179
是歌声
It's singing.

862
01:14:50,823 --> 01:14:53,621
我知道是歌声，但是谁在唱歌？
Yes, I realize it's singing. But who is singing?

863
01:14:54,594 --> 01:14:56,152
孩子们
The children.

864
01:14:59,031 --> 01:15:00,362
孩子们？
The children?

865
01:15:00,933 --> 01:15:03,663
我教了他们一首歌 欢迎男爵夫人
I taught them something to sing for the baroness.

866
01:15:09,308 --> 01:15:15,338
群山让我心充满音乐
My heart wants to sing Every song it hears

867
01:15:15,615 --> 01:15:18,175
要唱出每支歌
Every song that it hears

868
01:15:18,451 --> 01:15:23,889
我心震荡像鸟儿翅膀
My heart wants to beat like the wings Of the birds that rise

869
01:15:24,156 --> 01:15:27,284
由湖边飞上树
From the lake to the trees

870
01:15:27,526 --> 01:15:28,959
飞上树
To the trees

871
01:15:29,195 --> 01:15:34,132
我心叹息
My heart wants to sigh Like a chime that flies

872
01:15:34,333 --> 01:15:38,963
像钟声飘扬
From a church on a breeze

873
01:15:39,238 --> 01:15:43,140
笑声像小溪
To laugh like a brook When it trips and falls

874
01:15:43,409 --> 01:15:46,344
流过石头跌荡抑扬
Over stones on its way

875
01:15:46,646 --> 01:15:48,011
跌荡抑扬
On its way

876
01:15:48,247 --> 01:15:52,684
夜晚歌唱
To sing through the night

877
01:15:52,885 --> 01:15:58,551
像云雀祈祷
Like a lark who is learning to pray

878
01:15:58,824 --> 01:16:03,318
当我奔向山里
I go to the hills

879
01:16:03,529 --> 01:16:09,764
心情落寞
When my heart is lonely

880
01:16:10,036 --> 01:16:13,733
我听到…
I know I will hear

881
01:16:14,006 --> 01:16:19,774
昔日歌声
What I've heard before

882
01:16:20,613 --> 01:16:24,845
我心就会歌唱
My heart will be blessed

883
01:16:25,084 --> 01:16:32,047
因为音乐的响起
With the sound of music

884
01:16:32,925 --> 01:16:38,124
我要再度…
And I'll sing...

885
01:16:38,364 --> 01:16:46,464
歌唱
...once more

886
01:17:19,739 --> 01:17:21,502
雪绒花
Edelweiss!

887
01:17:25,478 --> 01:17:28,641
你从来没有告诉我 你的孩子们如此地可爱
You never told me how enchanting your children are.

888
01:17:37,256 --> 01:17:38,814
