他的歌声真响亮
Loud was the voice Of the lonely goatherd

907
01:19:15,020 --> 01:19:18,285
偏僻小镇的居民 亦听到他的歌声
Folks in a town That was quite remote heard

908
01:19:19,859 --> 01:19:23,090
他的歌声雄壮而清脆
Lusty and clear From the goatherd's throat heard

909
01:19:34,607 --> 01:19:37,474
犸塔！犸塔！
Marta. Marta!

910
01:19:39,879 --> 01:19:41,870
葛特儿，王子
Gretl, the prince!

911
01:19:43,616 --> 01:19:47,074
城堡的桥上有个王子听到了
A prince on the bridge Of a castle moat heard

912
01:19:48,554 --> 01:19:50,886
背着行囊上路的人们也听到了
Men on a road With a load to tote heard

913
01:19:53,392 --> 01:19:56,657
用膳中的人们也听到了
Men in the midst Of a table d'hote heard

914
01:19:57,997 --> 01:20:01,262
喝啤酒的人们也听到了
Men drinking beer With the foam afloat heard

915
01:20:12,344 --> 01:20:15,472
穿淡粉红色外衣的女孩也听见了
One little girl In a pale pink coat heard

916
01:20:17,116 --> 01:20:20,449
她唱歌回应那寂寞的牧羊人
She yodeled back To the lonely goatherd

917
01:20:21,620 --> 01:20:25,021
她妈妈也欣喜的唱着
Soon her mama With a gleaming gloat heard

918
01:20:26,525 --> 01:20:29,824
一个女孩和牧羊人 唱出多好的二重唱呀
What a duet for a girl and goatherd

919
