Soon her mama With a gleaming gloat heard

922
01:21:30,723 --> 01:21:33,851
一个女孩和牧羊人 唱出多好的二重唱呀
What a duet for a girl and goatherd

923
01:21:35,561 --> 01:21:37,188
他们多快乐啊
Happy are they

924
01:21:40,165 --> 01:21:43,430
二重唱将要成为三重唱
Soon the duet will become a trio

925
01:22:07,926 --> 01:22:09,518
-好极了！ -好极了！
- Bravo! - Bravo!

926
01:22:09,728 --> 01:22:11,218
好极了！
Very good!

927
01:22:13,032 --> 01:22:14,932
真精彩！
Wonderful!

928
01:22:15,534 --> 01:22:18,697
-麦斯伯伯，可以保留木偶吗？ -可以吗？
- Can we keep the puppets, Uncle Max? - Yes, can we?

929
01:22:18,904 --> 01:22:20,929
你当然可以，亲爱的
Of course you may, my darlings.

930
01:22:21,140 --> 01:22:25,372
不然，我怎能告诉可伦教授 将帐单寄给你父亲
Why else did I tell Professor Kohner to send the bill to your father?

931
01:22:29,114 --> 01:22:30,775
做得很好，小姐
Well done, fraulein.

932
01:22:33,285 --> 01:22:35,253
我真的很感动
I really am very much impressed.

933
01:22:35,454 --> 01:22:37,445
他们是你的孩子
They're your children, captain.

934
01:22:44,663 --> 01:22:46,961
你还有什么做不到的事吗？
My dear, is there anything you can't do?

935
01:22:47,232 --> 01:22:49,564
我不知自己能否成为好修女
Well, I'm not sure I'll make a good nun.

936
01:22:49,802 --> 01:22:52,896
如果有任何问题 我很乐意帮你的
If you have any problems, I'd be happy to help you.

937
01:22:56,008 --> 01:22:57,441
各位请注意
Attention, everyone!

938
01:22:57,643 --> 01:23:01,101
我有惊人的事情要宣布 惊喜！惊喜！
I have an announcement to make. Surprise! Surprise!

939
01:23:01,346 --> 01:23:03,644
经过一番苦心的寻求
Today, after a long and desperate search...

940
01:23:03,916 --> 01:23:08,910
我终于找到参加 萨尔斯堡音乐节的合唱团了
...I have found a most exciting entry for the Salzburg Folk Festival.

941
01:23:09,121 --> 01:23:10,952
恭喜你，麦斯
Congratulations, Max.

942
01:23:11,190 --> 01:23:14,159
这次是谁要给你利用呢？
And who will you be exploiting this time?

943
01:23:15,961 --> 01:23:19,158
-圣伊格森合唱团？ -再猜
- The Saint Ignatius Choir? - Guess again.

944
01:23:19,865 --> 01:23:23,801
我想，克兰曼歌团？
Well, let me see now. The Klopmann Choir?

945
01:23:24,036 --> 01:23:26,436
-不对，不对 -不对？
- No, no, no, no. - No, no?

946
01:23:26,638 --> 01:23:27,832
告诉我们
Tell us.

947
01:23:28,040 --> 01:23:31,498
一个由家庭组成的合唱团 你永远都不会估中的
A singing group all in one family. You'll never guess, Georg.

948
01:23:31,777 --> 01:23:34,678
多么好的主意
What a charming idea!

949
01:23:34,880 --> 01:23:36,677
谁的家庭？
Whose family?

950
01:23:37,549 --> 01:23:39,176
你的啊
Yours.

951
01:23:39,384 --> 01:23:41,716
他们将会是一大轰动
They'll be the talk of the festival.

952
01:23:44,556 --> 01:23:47,548
-有何好笑的？ -你很好笑，麦斯
- Well, now, what's so funny? - You are, Max.

953
01:23:47,826 --> 01:23:50,954
很昂贵，但很好笑
You're expensive, but very funny.

954
01:23:51,697 --> 01:23:54,029
-他们一定会相当轰动的 -不，麦斯
- They'll be a sensation! - No, Max.

955
01:23:54,299 --> 01:23:56,494
是极好的主意 新面孔又自然
It's a wonderful idea. Fresh, original.

956
01:23:56,702 --> 01:24:01,503
麦斯，我的孩子们不公开演唱
Max! My children do not sing in public.

957
01:24:02,174 --> 01:24:04,142
不能怪我没尝试过
You can't blame me for trying.

958
01:24:04,343 --> 01:24:07,335
孩子们，下一个该谁唱？
Children, who shall we hear from next?

959
01:24:10,149 --> 01:24:11,309
谁唱？
Who?

960
01:24:17,489 --> 01:24:18,683
对
Yes.

961
01:24:21,560 --> 01:24:23,494
全体一致通过
The vote is unanimous.

962
01:24:24,329 --> 01:24:25,887
由你演唱，舰长
You, captain.

963
01:24:26,165 --> 01:24:27,359
我？
Me?

964
01:24:28,200 --> 01:24:30,498
-我不懂 -拜托
- I don't understand. - Please.

965
01:24:36,708 --> 01:24:38,835
不…
No, no, no, no.

966
01:24:39,111 --> 01:24:41,170
我听说，很久以前 你唱的非常好
I'm told that you were quite good.

967
01:24:41,380 --> 01:24:44,679
-那是非常非常久之前 -我还记得，父亲
- That was a very, very long time ago. - I remember, Father.

968
01:24:44,917 --> 01:24:47,784
-请为我们唱一首 -求求你，父亲
- Play us something we know. - Oh, please, Father.

969
01:24:50,722 --> 01:24:51,780
这个…
Well...

970
01:25:02,034 --> 01:25:04,195
-你为何不告诉我？ -什么？
- Why didn't you tell me? - What?

971
01:25:04,469 --> 01:25:06,767
带我的口琴来
To bring along my harmonica.

972
