Bless my homeland forever

998
01:27:18,870 --> 01:27:22,533
只要你随时开口 就可以加入我的新节目
Anytime you say the word, Georg, you can be part of my new act:

999
01:27:22,741 --> 01:27:25,232
范崔普家庭合唱团
The von Trapp Family Singers.

1000
01:27:26,345 --> 01:27:28,836
我有个好主意
I have a wonderful idea, Georg.

1001
01:27:29,081 --> 01:27:31,549
让此屋中充满音乐
Let's really fill this house with music.

1002
01:27:31,783 --> 01:27:34,752
你要为我开个盛大的舞会
You must give a grand and glorious party for me.

1003
01:27:35,020 --> 01:27:37,716
-派对？ -是的，好吧，爸爸！
- A party? - Yes, Father, please!

1004
01:27:37,923 --> 01:27:40,289
我想我该认识 你在萨尔斯堡的朋友了
It's high time I met all your friends...

1005
01:27:40,592 --> 01:27:43,083
你不同意吗？
...and they met me. Don't you agree?

1006
01:27:43,362 --> 01:27:45,592
-我明白你的意思 -好吧，爸爸！
- I see what you mean. - Oh, please!

1007
01:27:45,864 --> 01:27:49,027
孩子们，该上床了 道晚安
Children, it's bedtime. Come now, say good night.

1008
01:27:49,968 --> 01:27:51,265
晚安，父亲
Good night, Father.

1009
01:27:51,470 --> 01:27:54,303
-晚安 -晚安，男爵夫人
- Good night. - Good night, Baroness Schraeder.

1010
01:27:54,539 --> 01:27:56,097
晚安，父亲
Good night, Father.

1011
01:27:59,077 --> 01:28:00,908
晚安，麦斯伯伯
Good night, Uncle Max.

1012
01:28:02,814 --> 01:28:05,977
